<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include(`${partials}/head`, {pageTitle: 'NFL Combine | Pro Day'}); -%>
<body>
    <%- include(`${partials}/menu`); -%>

    <div class="nfl-combine-pro-day" id="main-logo-container">
        <a href="<%= PP %>/">
            <img class="main-logo" src="<%= PP %>/images/logos/myocortex_logo_white.svg" alt="MYOCORTEX full logo">
        </a>
    </div>

    <section class="nfl-combine-pro-day top">
        <div class="filter"></div>
        <img class="mcx-logo" src="<%= PP %>/images/logos/mcx-dark-gray.png" alt="MCX White logo">
        <div class="textbox">
            <h1 class="title large">NFL Combine | <span class="pro-day">Pro Day</span></h1>
            <h1 class="title small">NFL Combine <span class="pro-day">Pro Day</span></h1>
            <p class="subtitle">8-week training program</p>
            <p class="subtitle date">Jan. 2 - Feb. 27</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#brag" class="down-arrow"><i class="fas fa-angle-down"></i></a>
    </section>

    <section class="nfl-combine-pro-day brag" id="brag">
        <div class="split-2">
            <div class="split-box image-container">
                <span miami-river-brickell title="Miami River Brickell"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="split-box textbox">
                <p>MCX is the only athletic training facility in the industry located in Downtown Miami, Miami’s bustling epicenter.  Walking distance to Brickell and three miles away from South Beach. Downtown Brickell Miami is truly the entertainment and international financial capital of the country.</p>
            </div>
            <img src="<%= PP %>/images/logos/mcx-dark-gray.png" alt="MCX Logo" class="mcx">
        </div>
        <div class="split-2">
            <div class="split-box textbox">
                <p>Being the most coveted address packed with gleaming skyscrapers, sweeping bay views, streets flooded with luxury retail, multicultural restaurants, clubs, bars, European sports cars, and young professionals with an average income that is twice that of the greater Miami area.  Sports professionals, bankers and executives all concentrated in a few zip codes provide access to opportunities at every moment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="split-box image-container">
                <span brickell-coast-night title="Brickell Coast at Night"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="split-2">
            <div class="split-box image-container">
                <span downtown-miami-night title="Downtown Miami at Night"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="split-box textbox">
                <p>If you need an escape, Brickell Key provides an escape a few blocks away where you can run or walk on an island with views of South Beach and Key Biscayne. Just like our process of training, coaching and educating is what got “Future Hall of Famer” Peyton Manning and “Hall of Famers” Randy Moss and Ray Lewis to a level of professional success, Downtown Brickell Miami is a high niche of people of prominence and celebrity. There is nothing like it…</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="nfl-combine-pro-day trent-saunders">
        <div class="split-2">
            <div class="split-box">
                <h3>Trent Saunders, OL</h3>
                <p>"The experience at MYOCORTEX is top of the line. They target muscles in the most interactive way with isolation and muscles technique exercises, that transfers to real power instead of compensated power allowing max performance. The only way to describe Myocortex it is a Game changer."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="split-box">
                <img src="<%= PP %>images/people/trent-saunders.jpg" alt="Trent Saunders">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="nfl-combine-pro-day path-to-the-draft">
        <div class="textbox">
            <h3>Path to the Draft</h3>
            <p>At MYOCORTEX, we have developed a proprietary regeneration phase in order to provide specific athlete-defined training programs. We hold ourselves accountable for every rep by checking our work before and after every session to ensure our athletes are progressing.</p>
            <p>Our goal is to build resiliency and durability while improving speed, strength, agility, explosive power, and endurance.</p>
        </div>
        <img class="footballers" src="<%= PP %>images/people/footballers.png" alt="footballers">
    </section>

    <section class="nfl-combine-pro-day medical">
        <img src="<%= PP %>/images/people/kneeling-stretch.png" alt="kneeling-stretch" class="kneeling-stretch">
        <h3>Medical</h3>
        <div class="textbox">
            <ul>
                <li>Concierge Physical Therapy</li>
                <li>Chiropractic Therapy</li>
                <li>Muscle Activation Techniques</li>
                <li>Massage Therapy</li>
                <li>Cupping</li>
                <li>Kinesio-tapping</li>
                <li>Myofascial Release</li>
                <li>Acupuncture</li>
                <li>Dry Needling</li>
            </ul>
            <ul>
                <li>Traditional Chinese Medicine (TCM) Acupuncture</li>
                <li>Ultrasound</li>
                <li>Low-energy Shockwave</li>
                <li>Platelet Rich Plasma (PRP)</li>
                <li>Adipose Stem Cells</li>
                <li>Adipose Bone Marrow Stem Cells</li>
                <li>Neurofunctional Electric and IV Therapy</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="nfl-combine-pro-day wonderlic">
        <h3>Wonderlic Test Interview Training Preparation</h3>
        <p>By working with our in-house Sports Psychologist, each athlete will get insight into the Wonderlic Test with test-taking strategies exclusively developed to maximize scores. In addition, they will work one on one to be prepared for team and media interviews.</p>
    </section>

