    <section class="nfl-combine-pro-day nutrition-support">
        <img class="vertical" src="<%= PP %>/images/backgrounds/vegetables-vertical.jpg" alt="vegetables">
        <img class="horizontal" src="<%= PP %>/images/backgrounds/vegetables-horizontal.jpg" alt="vegetables">
        <div class="textbox">
            <h3>Nutrition Support</h3>
            <p><b>Lush Meals Miami</b> will provide the athletes every day with freshly cooked organic food chosen to maximize muscle growth, fuel workouts, and decrease inflammation.</p>
            <p>Our proprietary recovery drink will be provided every day to decrease inflammation which will accelerate the recovery process.</p>
            <p>Protein shakes and performance supplements are powered by <b>ISAGENIX</b> who use dairy from grass-fed cows in New Zealand, free from banned substances tested by Informed Sport.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

