            <h3>Marlin Brooks, DB Ohio University</h3>
            <p>"I absolutely love working with MYOCORTEX. Their process has aided my technique and elevated my game to another level throughout high school and into prepping me for college. Every time I come home for break it is my priority to get into their facility to get my body worked on and to improve my skill."</p>
