    <section class="nfl-combine-pro-day mike-montero">
        <div class="filter"></div>
        <img src="<%= PP %>/images/people/mike-montero.jpg" alt="Mike Montero OL AAF">
        <div class="textbox">
            <h3>Mike Montero, OL</h3>
            <p>"My experience with MYOCORTEX has been only the best. I came in with muscle imbalances, but through MAT and a focus on muscle isolation, I have not only become stronger and faster, but also a stronger offensive lineman. I highly recommend MYOCORTEX if you want to step your game up to the next level."</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="nfl-combine-pro-day lodging-and-transportation">
        <div class="split-2">
            <div class="split-box textbox">
                <h3>Lodging and Transportation</h3>
                <p>We have contracted Habitat Residences-Condo Hotel, a family owned and operated facility for our 8-week program located just a few steps away from Miami's renowned financial center, Brickell Area, and the Miami metro.</p>
                <p>As a courtesy, they will provide the athletes with transportation to and from the training facility on all training days.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="split-box" habitat-residences-living-room title="Habitat Residences-Condo Hotel living room"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="split-3">
            <div class="split-box" habitat-residences-pool title="Habitat Residences-Condo Hotel pool"></div>
            <div class="split-box" habitat-residences-front title="Habitat Residences-Condo Hotel front"></div>
            <div class="split-box" habitat-residences-bed title="Habitat Residences-Condo Hotel bed"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="nfl-combine-pro-day support-at-indy">
        <div class="filter"></div>
        <h3 class="main-title">Support at Indy | Pro Day</h3>
        <p class="subtitle">Preparation is everything. Our staff will travel with the athletes to ensure that they have proper nutrient timing, are neurologically prepared, and to reinforce techniques practiced throughout our training period. <span class="no-wrap">(March 2-5, 2019)</span></p>
        <div class="split-4">
            <div class="split-box">
                <h4>Friday</h4>
                <p>TE, OL, PK, ST</p>
            </div>
            <div class="split-box">
                <h4>Saturday</h4>
                <p>QB, RB, WO</p>
            </div>
            <div class="split-box">
                <h4>Sunday</h4>
                <p>DL, LB, EDGE</p>
            </div>
            <div class="split-box">
                <h4>Monday</h4>
                <p>DB, S</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="nfl-combine-pro-day closing-statement">
        <h3>Closing Statement</h3>
        <p>We want to take this opportunity to thank you for considering MCX to coach your athlete. Our process is like no other company out there in the market. The athletes' physical and mental health is our number one priority to building a long-lasting career.</p>
        <p>Our program is limited to a small number of athletes in order to provide individual attention and superior quality. Accountability is everything!</p>
    </section>

    <section class="nfl-combine-pro-day cta">
        <div class="filter"></div>
        <div class="text">
            <h4 class="appear">NFL Combine | Pro Day</h4>
            <a href="<%= PP %>/sign-up" class="btn appear sign-up-btn">sign up</a>
            <img src="<%= PP %>/images/logos/mcx-contrast-dark.png" class="logo" />
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include(`${partials}/footer`, {classNames: ''}); -%>
    <%- include(`${partials}/scripts`); -%>
</body>
</html>
